mages%2F3476712%2Forg%2Fda1107353c2aae2433dbf87b3fc07f9d.jpg%2FthCitdbe8Q2m5HR42QjkFsnaJg8jZEFp7bMEzMezBMw&h=d13fdb42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3476711/org/412b30078a52cb520ce18d0675e35ddd.jpg/0HUjwNKDWSDg7qKHHt8TY2CGwHqROubusZ4ee5ueHns\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3476711%2Forg%2F412b30078a52cb520ce18d0675e35ddd.jpg%2F0HUjwNKDWSDg7qKHHt8TY2CGwHqROubusZ4ee5ueHns&h=43094dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3476708/org/8d755e87f2047245554be815df1ef40e.jpg/X1gkokQ3O_YhlU8kBd4oqB8kTDAWiCIpgDQX8Ko0F_A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3476708%2Forg%2F8d755e87f2047245554be815df1ef40e.jpg%2FX1gkokQ3O_YhlU8kBd4oqB8kTDAWiCIpgDQX8Ko0F_A&h=0d697cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3476709/org/97e46397b00f757f5f318cd9bb03241f.jpg/GYULGuOB2tcbBbkajXSGxIbdkAQitolW0kL00_hC9NM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3476709%2Forg%2F97e46397b00f757f5f318cd9bb03241f.jpg%2FGYULGuOB2tcbBbkajXSGxIbdkAQitolW0kL00_hC9NM&h=19c05090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐天佑和黃又南訪問各有各做，非常尷尬。（葉志明攝）<br />\n<br />\n談到二人關係，黃又南接受《香港01》訪問時親自解說：「其實好多人都會問我同天佑究竟咩關係？其實喺今年年頭，其實我哋公司同天佑大家都有一個方案，其實係想大家分開發展，好似天佑佢想做返自己嘅音樂，我自己亦想專注喺電影及音樂方面嘅工作，其實之前我經理人公司都回答過。」<br />\n<br />\n問是否因政見立場不和？又南答謂：「我相信唔會因為呢樣嘢，我哋唔會因為呢啲嘢鬧交，我哋而家絕對係朋友。（為何剛才見到你哋在台上眼神零交流，沒有碰杯？）大家太敏感啦，千祈唔好咁諗，頭先佢在台上講嘢嘅時候，因為我要照顧旁邊嘅小朋友，因為佢同我講佢好緊張，所以係咁啫。」<br />\n<br />\n黃又南指自己與徐天佑仍然是朋友。（葉志明攝）<br />\n<br />\n問為何與黃又南分開做訪問？天佑受訪時表示：「其實呢啲嘢喺社交網站都解釋得清清白白嘅，咁不過可能大家對我當時講個句『No More Shine』有啲疑問，當時我冇回應到，但公司經理人幫我回應咗，咁而家要我夾硬去再去解答我所講嘅嘢，自己始終都覺得對公司都好唔尊重，咁就用公司嘅答案啦。」談到兩人零交流時，天佑坦言雙方感陌生：「我哋好耐冇見，直頭聯絡都冇聯絡過，起碼成大半年都冇電話聯絡，今日下午做訪問先見返。」<br />\n<br />\n徐天佑直言與黃又南一段時間沒有聯絡。（葉志明攝）<br />\n<br />\n撰文：吳子生<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/392041/no-more-shine-%E5%BE%8C%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%90%8C%E5%A0%B4%E5%8B%81%E5%B0%B7%E5%B0%AC-%E5%BE%90%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91-%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%88%E5%8D%97%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%AD%E5%86%87%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F392041%2Fno-more-shine-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%258B%2581%25E5%25B0%25B7%25E5%25B0%25AC-%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BD%2591-%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%258F%2588%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A1&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=3f1bf88a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/392041/no-more-shine-%E5%BE%8C%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%90%8C%E5%A0%B4%E5%8B%81%E5%B0%B7%E5%B0%AC-%E5%BE%90%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91-%E5%90%8C%E5%8F%88%E5%8D%97%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%AD%E5%86%87%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1</a>"},{"pid":"e3b499d5df752c1629db677efeb92fc88bc4a076","tid":1681773,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPMCZAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPMCZAr.jpg&h=a189dd43&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e5b5e3f5b21c9a00b242aa4894780033fe22742c","tid":1681773,"uid":247905,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"唔怪得天佑靚仔過另一件騎呢怪咁多<br />\n原來有得解釋"},{"pid":"7dc08d1185d027f5fa9580c94ddf74e47366c09d","tid":1681773,"uid":57490,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"e5b5e3f5b21c9a00b242aa4894780033fe22742c","tid":1681773,"uid":247905,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"唔怪得天佑靚仔過另一件騎呢怪咁多<br />\n原來有得解釋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"相由身心 乜撚野又南柒到嘔"},{"pid":"07acbbb8420fb785c267b9a0c92dde5789d52773","tid":1681773,"uid":228143,"like":22,"dislike":